<caption>"How Big Is the US Debt? (360 Video)" by the Institute for Humane Studies</caption></figure></para><para id="delete_me"><title>Description</title>The US government debt is now bigger than the debt of any other government in human history. It is so big, that it is hard to comprehend just how big it is. This immersive 360 degree video helps illustrate the scale of the debt while Professor Antony Davies from Duquesne University breaks down the debt and explains its implications. The video can be watched on computers, smartphones for on-the-go learning, or virtual reality headsets for a fully immersive experience. Use your mouse or move your phone around to move around the video.</para><para id="eip-781"><title>Watch on YouTube</title><link url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErUZjM16r1M" window="new">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErUZjM16r1M</link></para></content>

